    <item>
      <title>美国小企业乐观情绪跌至 11 年来最低点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-09/us-small-business-optimism-falls-to-a-more-than-11-year-low</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据全国独立企业联合会的数据，由于销售预期下滑和通胀压力仍然是一个麻烦问题，3 月份美国小企业的乐观情绪跌至 11 年多以来的最低点。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-09/us-small-business-optimism-falls-to-a-more-than-11-year-low</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>津巴布韦的 ZiG 货币在首次亮相后第二天就走强，尽管它扰乱了商业</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-09/zimbabwe-s-new-zig-currency-strengthens-on-second-day-of-trading</link>
      <description><![CDATA[津巴布韦新的黄金支持货币 ZiG 在首次亮相一天后就走强，尽管银行、零售商和公用事业公司都在争先恐后地转向使用新货币，从而扰乱了全国商业。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-09/zimbabwe-s-new-zig-currency-strengthens-on-second-day-of-trading</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 06:58:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>黑石集团即将收购护肤品公司欧舒丹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-09/blackstone-said-to-near-buyout-of-skin-care-company-l-occitane</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士称，欧舒丹国际公司 (L&#39;Occitane International SA) 的亿万富翁所有者 Reinold Geiger 即将达成协议，在黑石公司 (Blackstone Inc.) 的资金帮助下将这家护肤品公司私有化，这可能会结束该公司在香港证券交易所 14 年的连续上市。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-09/blackstone-said-to-near-buyout-of-skin-care-company-l-occitane</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 01:51:13 GMT</pubDate>
